'''The Lost''' is an article written by [[Morrie Mullins (real person)|Morrie Mullins]] as a tie in to the [[Living Force (roleplaying campaign)|Living Force]] campaign. It was published on the [[Wizards of the Coast]] website on [[February 13]] [[2003]] and took the form of a presentation by Jedi [[Lora Nadad]] on [[The Lost (children)|the Lost]], homeless children in the [[Cularin system/Legends|Cularin system]].

